							</SELECT>
						</TD>
					</TR>
					<TR>
						<TD ALIGN="left" VALIGN="top">
							<FONT SIZE=-1>choose which template to use for formatting the contents of the message.  If you are sending mail to a pager, choose one of the "short" templates.</FONT>
